  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0003",
    "kind": "text_cluster_panel",
    "page": "yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0",
    "primary_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_7",
    "source": "text_cluster",
    "member_count": 1,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Over the last two years, tax administrations globally have assumed new roles with ingenuity and skill.From launching digital platforms to serve struggling businesses to partnering with social services to deliver benefits, they've dramatically upped the pace of digital transformation. They've also recognized that digital will be key to meeting their challenges, including uncertain revenue projections and the growing need to finance budget deficits.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5086658605401048,
          0.6344591705857204,
          0.9488109633212415,
          0.7376371668804332
        ],
        "order": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0004",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0",
    "primary_id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_3",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 7,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_3",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "In brief",
        "bbox": [
          0.060459492140266025,
          0.6515604959384352,
          0.11769447803305119,
          0.6646715120421832
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Tax administrations know that digital transformation is necessary. But its potential extends far beyond fighting fires in a pandemic to improving life for citizens.",
        "bbox": [
          0.058847239016525596,
          0.6812027932164743,
          0.46594115276098347,
          0.7439076528430953
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But digital transformation can help tax administrations do much more than fight fires and solve problems. It has the potential to transform them from reactive, passive recipients of tax returns into proactive partners in improving how businesses operate and people live.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5086658605401048,
          0.7490380504489098,
          0.9439742039500202,
          0.821433661108736
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Tax administrators can realize big benefits by designing customer-centric services, integrating digital into modernization programs and exchanging data in real time.",
        "bbox": [
          0.058847239016525596,
          0.7621490665526578,
          0.46271664651350264,
          0.8254239703577028
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Tax administrations won't achieve this by adopting and embedding new digital technologies alone. To truly transform, they need to put taxpayers at the center of their digital journey and integrate their plans into wider digital government programs.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5086658605401048,
          0.8334045888556363,
          0.9528415961305925,
          0.8915490950548668
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Choosing the right operating model, systems, partners and performance measures will be important steps on the road to transformation success.",
        "bbox": [
          0.058847239016525596,
          0.8430953398888413,
          0.4191858121725111,
          0.9058001995154624
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_ey-digital-state-tax-article.pdf_0_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "This article, the second in the series on the digital state, suggests five ways they can do this.",
        "bbox": [
          0.5086658605401048,
          0.9023799344449195,
          0.9463925836356308,
          0.9308821433661109
        ],
        "order": 11
      }
    ]
  }
]